I";<p>This is a publication made within the framework of <em>Searching for the European Roller</em>. Including archival material, photographs (both found and new), notes and thoughts, the publication begins its journey on Fårö in 1968 and continues through time and place toward southern latitudes in a search and understanding of a bird’s disappearance and departure.</p>

